The,LanguageTool,is,an,open,source,project,that,proofreads,and,checks,text,for,spelling,style,and,grammar,mistakes,in,a,variety,of,languages,The,tool,can,be,used,online,or,downloaded,for,other,use,The,LanguageTool,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,LanguageTool,with,other,applications,The,main,API,method,is,checking,text,for,spelling,grammar,and,style,mistakes